'''Judith Kanakuze''' (yavutse  Ku ya 19 Nzeri 1959 - yapfuye Ku ya 7 Gashyantare 2010 )) yarumunyapolitiki [[Rwanda|wu Rwanda]] numunyarwandakazi . Yamaze gukora mu nzego nyinshi, zirimo imirire ndetse na serivisi rusange, yabaye umunyapolitiki uzwi nyuma ya [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|jenoside y'Abatutsi mu Rwanda]] mu 1994, aho yabuze abavandimwe benshi <ref>https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Guardian</ref> .Kanakuze yashinze ihuriro Réseau des Femmes kandi arengera uburenganzira bw’umugore mu gihe cy’amasezerano ya Arusha . Yatorewe kuba [[Inteko Ishinga Amategeko y’u Rwanda|inteko ishinga amategeko y'u Rwanda]] mu 2003 na 2008. Muri manda ye, yayoboye ''Rwanda Women Parliamentary Forum''  .

== Amateka ==
Judith Kanakuze yavutse19 septembre 1959Ku ya 19 Nzeri 1959 mu Karere ka [[Akarere ka Rusizi|Rusizi]], mu Rwanda. Umwarimu imyaka ibiri mu ntangiriro ya za 1980, nyuma yaje kuba inzobere mu mirire .<ref>https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Guardian</ref> Judith akaba yarabuze abavandimwe benshi muri Genocide yakorewe abatutsi 1994 , biciwe  mu rusengero rwa Kibuye <ref name="McGreal">https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Guardian</ref> .

Nyuma y’amakimbirane, yasubiye mu Rwanda avuye mu nkambi y’impunzi i Goma kugira ngo yugurure ihuriro ry’inguzanyo ry’abagore ry’inzobere mu micungire y’imari ndetse anatanga gahunda yo kwigisha no gukemura amakimbirane. Kanakuze yashinze umuryango w’abagore bo hambere Réseau des Femmes<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_New_Times_(Rwanda)</ref> akaba yari umujyanama mu mpera za 90. Kanakuze yarazwi nk'umuyobozi uharanira uburenganzira bw'umugore mu Rwanda, yatoranijwe kugira ngo akore muri komisiyo ishinzwe itegekonshinga ryo mu 2001 mu rwego rwo guharanira uburinganire.<ref>https://doi.org/10.1093%2Fafraf%2Fadn024</ref><ref>https://scholarworks.gsu.edu/anthro_facpub/2</ref><ref>https://www.theguardian.com/world/2008/dec/17/rwanda-women-politics-humnan-rights</ref>n'umwe mubagore batatu waruri kumwnaya wabantu 12.Yatanze ibitekerezo byinshi bijyanye n’uburinganire mu itegeko nshinga, icy'ingenzi muri byo kikaba cyarashyizeho ibipimo by’uburinganire aho abagore bagomba gushyiraho nibura 30% by’imyanya ku nzego zifata ibyemezo mu Rwanda<ref>https://doi.org/10.1093%2Fafraf%2Fadn024</ref><ref>https://scholarworks.gsu.edu/anthro_facpub/2</ref><ref>https://www.theguardian.com/world/2008/dec/17/rwanda-women-politics-humnan-rights</ref>Imiryango itegamiye kuri leta y’abagore n’abagore ku giti cyabo bongereye Kanakuze kugira ngo bumvishe abandi bagize komisiyo. Abagore bo mu Rwanda batangiye kwinjira muri komite zigenzurwa n’abagabo kandi bamenyekana ku bindi bibazo bitari uburinganire. Kugeza mu 2003, abagore bari bafite kimwe cya kabiri cy'imyanya mu Nteko Ishinga Amategeko <ref>https://academic.oup.com/afraf/article/107/428/361/12456?login=false</ref>maze Kanakuze atorerwa umwe muri bo.<ref>https://www.inclusivesecurity.org/experts/judith-kanakuze/</ref>
